			<item>kiḻ-pā<supplied reason="omitted">ṟ</supplied>kk' ellai <hi rend="grantha">de</hi>va-tāṉam nal Araicūr Ellai <unclear>mē</unclear><choice><sic>n=ku</sic><corr>ṟku</corr></choice>m piṭākai ciṟu-pāttu Ellaikku me<supplied reason="omitted">ṟ</supplied>kkum</item>
			
